<h2>The Liber elegantiarum by Joan Esteve (Monographie)</h2>
<h3>A Catalan-Latin dictionary at the crossroads of fifteenth-century European culture</h3>
<hr>
<abbr class='unapi-id' title='1919'></abbr>
